commit.message:
pa.h (reg_class): Add new NON_SHIFT_REGS class.

	* pa.h (reg_class): Add new NON_SHIFT_REGS class.
	(REG_CLASS_NAMES): Name new class "NON_SHIFT_REGS".
	(REG_CLASS_CONTENTS): Initialize NON_SHIFT_REGS.
